{"tid":2072710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[推到全香港都識]一分鐘帶你認識義勇軍進行曲","createTime":"2020-06-20T18:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T09:22:57.000Z","uid":70029,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0cea79bc4d09a18021c4a7db631eac032368dac4","tid":2072710,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"適逢國歌法既實施，作為香港人點可以唔認識一下義勇軍進行曲？<br />\n利申：我岩岩先背，憑記憶背默返出黎，希望無錯<br />\n歌詞如下<br />\n起來！不願做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">奴隸</span></span>的人們<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新的</span></span>長城！<br />\n中華民<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國</span></span>到了最<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">危險</span></span>的時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人</span></span>被迫著發出最後的吼聲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">起來! 起來! 起來!</span></span><br />\n我們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">萬眾一心</span></span>, 冒著敵人的炮火前進!<br />\n冒著<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敵人的炮火</span></span>前進! 前進! 前進, 進!<br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得睇住MV學 容易學習<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zbxnPQTl0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3zbxnPQTl0w&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=deb035d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zbxnPQTl0w</a><br />\n順便一提 條MV點擊率同LIKE太少　證明無乜香港人睇過　要推廣下比大家<br />\n<br />\n認識完歌詞同MV 點少得認識作詞人田漢 太長唔COPY出黎 總之就係比中國文革批鬥死左<br />\n有性趣既自己禁入去睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%94%B0%E6%B1%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E6%25B1%2589&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a40b7d68\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%94%B0%E6%B1%89</a><br />\n<br />\n有餘力既 希望大家可以轉載以上既內容<br />\n順便用任何方法實現義勇軍進行曲既內容 以尊重國家 以及維護國家安全 出一分力"},{"pid":"908d439a9aae81e09e8dc5cbd6f58cd64daad883","tid":2072710,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實有得唸，<br />\n不過會俾人話on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6234c1dbe712c4611ffeb16c9060173a9e32c9b","tid":2072710,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"你老婆琴日陪我訓覺"},{"pid":"0121ca4f9b6d9215c28cefc3f0e0f6891ce29a02","tid":2072710,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"908d439a9aae81e09e8dc5cbd6f58cd64daad883","tid":2072710,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實有得唸，<br />\n不過會俾人話on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"有咩咁ON9....?"},{"pid":"4a318aa6b03a702cf280cb551ec3b697215272a1","tid":2072710,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0121ca4f9b6d9215c28cefc3f0e0f6891ce29a02","tid":2072710,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"908d439a9aae81e09e8dc5cbd6f58cd64daad883","tid":2072710,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實有得唸，<br />\n不過會俾人話on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"有咩咁ON9....?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"冇嘢on9<br />\n不過實有連登仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2f0294a17ddbc439c986763892d7aa8ca8e928","tid":2072710,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a318aa6b03a702cf280cb551ec3b697215272a1","tid":2072710,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0121ca4f9b6d9215c28cefc3f0e0f6891ce29a02","tid":2072710,"uid":70029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu